  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You carve glowing runes into your skin, dealing 3 damage to yourself even if you fail to perform this technique. The seal activates instinctively whenever anyone tries to apply a seal to you, such as by a sealing technique or a crafted item (exploding tag, sealing tag, etc). When activated, the seal deals 5 points of damage to the creature applying the seal (techniques) or the item applied (which most likely destroys the item before it can activate). If a technique was attempted, the attacker must make an opposed level check against you. If you succeed, the seal will not be applied. After the seal activates, it vanishes. You can concentrate for an attack action to suppress the seal's effects for one round.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 5 Chakra and deal yourself double damage to allow this seal to activate twice before it vanishes.</p>\n\n",
